            .Grid.Grid--gutters.Grid--full.large-Grid--fit
              .Grid-cell.Grid-cell--top
                ul.info
                  li
                    | Applications are open until June 21 and exhibitors will be selected and notified on a rolling basis.
                  li PWYC table fee: Suggested ~ $20 for half-table, $40 for full table
                  li The venue is air-conditioned and barrier-free.
                  li High-speed wi-fi is available.
                  li You'll get half or all of a 6-foot table, power and 2 chairs.
                  li
                    strong What we're looking for from games exhibitors:
                    |  Video games, board games, card games, tabletop games, artist collectives, tiny/weird interactive things and VR experiences are all welcome. Bring a complete version or playable demo
                    b plus
                    |  one-of-a-kind, handmade/DIY
                    |                   items, boxed games, or other physical treasures to sell. We have outdoor space, too, if your game is neant to be played in a park!
                  li
